{"type": "article", "id": 4622, "title": "Ivetta 摇摇椅", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-23T07:58:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233414xSbZAyPjJzo0pFGB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利家居设计品牌 Formabilio 今年邀请来自罗马的设计师 Giancarlo Cutello 为其设计了一款名为「Ivetta」的椅子，选用了意大利本土的山毛榉木，并用毛毡将椅背和扶手进行包裹，垫衬部分通过木钉固定，方便拆解更换。如果配置摇杆的话，则可以轻松变身俏皮的摇摇椅。无摇杆款定价 298 欧元（约合人民币 2272 元），配置摇杆款定价 356 欧元（约合人民币 2715 元），提供海洋蓝与黑米色混色两种选择，<a href=\"https://www.formabilio.com/shop\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233412Ptb4iaomkz7TgrdF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233412P0biLU1Ctazvw28p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233413vuDPZcSxkg3Li91F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233413kEpvhRtUP04NKLSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233413RfFvgA5wry3IK0Z6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.753125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}